{"tid":2173524,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"而家做人得返移民一個心願","createTime":"2020-08-25T09:40:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T10:31:31.000Z","uid":58316,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7c5cae7c16fcf98c1aab95c07b2fbc0b0cc1ffbf","tid":2173524,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T09:40:00.000Z","msg":"返工只為儲錢<br />\n唔望有得升<br />\n冇人生規劃<br />\n儲錢炒股票<br />\n得就得<br />\n攞舊錢去外國學店讀master<br />\n唔得就返黎捱過<br />\n返工<br />\n炒股<br />\n總之以移民為依歸<br />\n所有野都係賭博<br />\n好似以前個代<br />\n走難落黎個d<br />\n途中冇命既不計其數<br />\n100年前<br />\n過美國起火車軌個d<br />\n借錢搭船<br />\n又要貼錢打工<br />\n但人地都過去<br />\n有時諗<br />\n依個世界真係分幾層<br />\n金字塔頂<br />\n就係外國<br />\n識投胎比人奮鬥少幾十年<br />\n依幾十年可能就係你一世"},{"pid":"38b0664c41fdc7909959a76bc282e1dc2e1ec9c2","tid":2173524,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T09:44:29.000Z","msg":"Yes"},{"pid":"7497262626dff982f898f7215b1e71177e4c2ba6","tid":2173524,"uid":65638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T09:44:37.000Z","msg":"樓主你做鬼佬但153cm,肯唔肯"},{"pid":"b9e8581ba689b82466d17de7b304eea5d607127f","tid":2173524,"uid":158899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7497262626dff982f898f7215b1e71177e4c2ba6","tid":2173524,"uid":65638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T09:44:37.000Z","msg":"樓主你做鬼佬但153cm,肯唔肯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T10:31:31.000Z","msg":"有父幹怕咩做 100億 最少"}]}